.SH NAME
octane - OCTANE — OCPP conformance test runner


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBoctane [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
octane runs .story suites against a CSMS endpoint, validates
story files, and manages the content-addressed result cache.

.PP
Global flags apply to all subcommands. Use "octane help "
for subcommand-specific documentation.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--cache-dir\fP=""
	override the cache directory (default: $XDG_CACHE_HOME/octane/cache)

.PP
\fB--config\fP="octane.yml"
	path to octane.yml configuration file

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for octane

.PP
\fB--no-cache\fP[=false]
	bypass the result cache entirely

.PP
\fB-v\fP, \fB--verbose\fP[=false]
	enable verbose output


